South Africa’s Sports Minister Collapses in Cabinet Meeting, New Age Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-26T05:01:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/south-african-sports-minister-collapses-in-cabinet-meeting-new-age-says.html
South African Sports Minister Fikile
Mbalula collapsed during a Cabinet meeting yesterday, The New
Age said, citing government spokesman Jimmy Manyi.  The 40-year-old minister should be back at work today after
recovering from the “sudden flu-like symptoms,” the
Johannesburg-based newspaper cited Manyi as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  